07:04.091 --> 07:06.343
You're going to visit Grandma?

07:06.385 --> 07:07.928
No, a different part of Canada.

07:07.969 --> 07:10.764
Someplace wild where people

07:07.969 --> 07:10.764
don't have to destroy love

07:10.805 --> 07:12.974
