07:13.016 --> 07:14.726
You just ran away from school?

07:14.768 --> 07:16.937
Mom's really going

07:14.768 --> 07:16.937
to kill you now.

07:16.978 --> 07:19.064
No, she won't,

07:16.978 --> 07:19.064
because she won't know.

07:19.106 --> 07:20.941
Malcolm, you can't

07:19.106 --> 07:20.941
tell anybody.

07:20.982 --> 07:23.484
I'm placing my life

07:20.982 --> 07:23.484
in your hands here.

07:23.526 --> 07:25.987
Did you roll around

07:23.526 --> 07:25.987
in something?

07:26.029 --> 07:27.781
You'll get used to it.

07:27.822 --> 07:29.324
Look, I need you

07:27.822 --> 07:29.324
to get Beebee

07:29.366 --> 07:30.491
to come see me

07:29.366 --> 07:30.491
tonight, okay?

07:30.533 --> 07:31.743
Give her this.

07:31.785 --> 07:33.578
Let it air out

07:31.785 --> 07:33.578
for a while first.

07:33.620 --> 07:35.538
Try to get me some food,

07:35.580 --> 07:38.417
'cause I haven't eaten

07:35.580 --> 07:38.417
