But...

07:49.552 --> 07:50.887
Can I trust you?

07:50.929 --> 07:53.432
Yes.

07:53.473 --> 07:55.016
Yeah, definitely.

07:56.810 --> 07:59.229
I'll toss my lunch bag

07:56.810 --> 07:59.229
