09:04.794 --> 09:07.172
I don't know what to do.

09:07.214 --> 09:09.632
Squeal.

09:09.674 --> 09:10.842
What?

09:10.884 --> 09:12.093
Squeal.

09:12.135 --> 09:14.388
Rat him out.

09:14.429 --> 09:15.596
I can't do that.

09:15.638 --> 09:17.057
He's my brother.

09:17.098 --> 09:18.433
I promised him.

09:18.475 --> 09:20.310
I can't tell anybody.

09:20.352 --> 09:22.854
You told... me.

09:22.896 --> 09:24.647
Yeah, but by the time

09:22.896 --> 09:24.647
you tell anyone,

09:24.689 --> 09:26.233
