09:26.274 --> 09:29.444
Tou... ché.

09:33.948 --> 09:35.492
Beebee?

09:35.534 --> 09:36.493
What?

09:36.535 --> 09:38.619
Oh, you're, uh, that kid.

09:38.661 --> 09:39.996
My name's Malcolm.

09:40.038 --> 09:41.456
I'm Francis's brother.

09:41.498 --> 09:43.417
You met me, like,

09:41.498 --> 09:43.417
ten times.

09:43.458 --> 09:47.128
Yeah, you're the freaky

09:43.458 --> 09:47.128
little brain, right?

09:48.922 --> 09:49.881
Just be cool.

09:49.923 --> 09:51.091
What do you want?

09:51.132 --> 09:52.633
Here.

09:52.675 --> 09:54.010
Francis is back home.

09:54.052 --> 09:56.263
Well, he's not home.

09:54.052 --> 09:56.263
He's hiding.

09:56.304 --> 09:58.639
Huh. Three pages?

09:58.681 --> 10:00.559
Both sides.

10:00.600 --> 10:02.643
He loves to make me read.

10:02.685 --> 10:04.438
What's that word?

10:04.479 --> 10:05.688
"Consummate."

10:06.856 --> 10:08.649
It means he likes you.

10:08.691 --> 10:10.610
Oh.

10:13.280 --> 10:16.657
"Assignation,

10:13.280 --> 10:16.657
rendezvous, tryst"?

10:16.699 --> 10:19.494
How the hell is anyone supposed

10:16.699 --> 10:19.494
to know what he's talking about?

10:19.536 --> 10:21.662
Beebee, just meet him at

10:19.536 --> 10:21.662
the creek at 7:30, okay?

10:21.704 --> 10:25.833
See? You can say it in English,

10:21.704 --> 10:25.833
and you're, like, ten.

10:25.875 --> 10:26.960
What are you doing?!

10:27.001 --> 10:28.253
I'm wearing a tank top.

10:28.295 --> 10:29.670
Beebee, I don't...

10:29.712 --> 10:30.713
Don't think.

10:30.755 --> 10:32.382
Just walk. Go.

10:43.226 --> 10:46.646
The worst part is, I think

10:43.226 --> 10:46.646
I'm stealing panty liners.

10:47.772 --> 10:50.066
Gosh, I had such

10:47.772 --> 10:50.066
a good day at work today.

10:50.108 --> 10:51.692
I got to work

10:50.108 --> 10:51.692
the cash-only line

10:51.734 --> 10:53.111
for the first time

10:51.734 --> 10:53.111
in a month,

10:53.153 --> 10:55.280
and my register

10:53.153 --> 10:55.280
came out to the penny.

10:55.322 --> 10:57.574
Plus, that creepy new

10:55.322 --> 10:57.574
assistant manager

10:57.616 --> 10:59.700
sliced his hand open

10:57.616 --> 10:59.700
with a box cutter.

10:59.742 --> 11:02.579
Spent the whole afternoon

10:59.742 --> 11:02.579
in the emergency room.

11:02.621 --> 11:05.165
Here's to him.

11:05.206 --> 11:07.708
Honey, this chicken

11:05.206 --> 11:07.708
