Oh, well, it's a little recipe

11:07.750 --> 11:10.128
I came up with.

11:10.170 --> 11:12.130
It's Shake n' Bake--

11:10.170 --> 11:12.130
but for pork.

11:12.172 --> 11:14.007
How about that?

11:14.048 --> 11:17.427
That's one for the recipe box.

11:17.469 --> 11:18.928
Let's call it, uh, "chork."

11:18.970 --> 11:20.679
All in favor?

11:21.598 --> 11:23.391
No one for "picken"?

11:23.433 --> 11:24.518
Chork it is.

11:24.559 --> 11:25.726
Brava.

11:25.768 --> 11:27.521
Oh, cut it out.

11:27.562 --> 11:29.564
You big talker.

