You haven't had a bite in

11:44.703 --> 11:46.747
two minutes, I counted.

11:46.789 --> 11:47.748
I'm saving it.

11:47.790 --> 11:49.668
There is no saving.

11:49.708 --> 11:50.751
Malcolm, he's right.

11:50.793 --> 11:52.711
The rule is: no saving.

11:53.880 --> 11:56.257
Oh, yeah, I care.

11:53.880 --> 11:56.257
Cut it out!

11:56.299 --> 11:57.758
(phone ringing)

11:56.299 --> 11:57.758
Come on, it's mine.

11:57.800 --> 11:59.010
Get out of here!

11:57.800 --> 11:59.010
No!

11:59.052 --> 12:00.595
Give it back!

11:59.052 --> 12:00.595
Boys, boys, stop it.

12:00.637 --> 12:01.804
You're going get

12:00.637 --> 12:01.804
your mother out of...

12:01.846 --> 12:04.182
uh, you're going to ruin

12:01.846 --> 12:04.182
her nice day.

12:04.224 --> 12:05.766
Francis did what?!

12:09.396 --> 12:12.065
Another night in the chat room.

12:17.111 --> 12:18.572
That kid! That kid!

12:18.613 --> 12:20.156
He thinks he can just

12:18.613 --> 12:20.156
run away from school

12:20.198 --> 12:21.575
like some-some kind

12:20.198 --> 12:21.575
of escaped convict?

12:21.616 --> 12:23.159
Well, if he thinks

12:21.616 --> 12:23.159
he can just vanish

12:23.201 --> 12:25.078
in the night

12:23.201 --> 12:25.078
and I won't find him,

12:25.119 --> 12:26.787
well, he is sadly mistaken.

12:26.829 --> 12:27.872
Lois, you just calm down.

12:27.914 --> 12:29.957
There's nothing

12:27.914 --> 12:29.957
we can do right now.

12:29.999 --> 12:31.959
Yes, there is.

12:29.999 --> 12:31.959
I can call the police.

12:32.001 --> 12:33.794
No, they're not going

12:32.001 --> 12:33.794
to look for anybody

12:33.836 --> 12:35.796
unless they've been missing

12:33.836 --> 12:35.796
for 48 hours.

12:35.838 --> 12:37.798
Not if I say he has

12:35.838 --> 12:37.798
drugs on him.

12:37.840 --> 12:39.300
Lois, stop it.

12:39.342 --> 12:41.219
Now, you're just going

12:39.342 --> 12:41.219
to have to accept the fact

12:41.261 --> 12:43.221
that for now, this is

12:41.261 --> 12:43.221
beyond your control.

12:43.263 --> 12:45.473
Francis is going to have

12:43.263 --> 12:45.473
to sink or swim on his own,

12:45.515 --> 12:48.476
and frankly, I don't think

12:45.515 --> 12:48.476
that's such a bad thing.

12:48.518 --> 12:51.312
And in the meantime, we just

12:48.518 --> 12:51.312
have to leave it up to fate.

12:51.354 --> 12:53.231
Oh. "Fate."

12:53.273 --> 12:56.025
"Fate" is just what you call it

12:53.273 --> 12:56.025
when you don't know the name

12:56.067 --> 12:58.319
of the person

12:56.067 --> 12:58.319
screwing you over!

13:02.865 --> 13:05.702
Mom, I'm sure he's okay.

13:07.495 --> 13:09.664
Uh-oh, tactical error.

13:09.706 --> 13:11.750
Why do you think he's okay, son?

13:11.790 --> 13:14.877
Because...

13:11.790 --> 13:14.877
he's always okay.

13:16.045 --> 13:17.838
Malcolm,

13:17.880 --> 13:19.840
this is a very serious

13:17.880 --> 13:19.840
situation here,

13:19.882 --> 13:22.719
and, well, I know you love

13:19.882 --> 13:22.719
Francis as much as we do,

13:22.761 --> 13:23.844
so if you have

13:23.886 --> 13:25.305
any idea...

13:25.346 --> 13:27.848
Oh, for God's sake!

13:25.346 --> 13:27.848
Where is he?!

13:27.890 --> 13:29.517
He came here to see Beebee!

13:27.890 --> 13:29.517
He's meeting her tonight!

13:29.559 --> 13:31.311
Oh, my God,

13:29.559 --> 13:31.311
how'd she do that?

13:31.352 --> 13:32.353
I knew it.

13:32.395 --> 13:33.854
When did you talk to him?

13:33.896 --> 13:35.148
Don't look at her eyes,

13:33.896 --> 13:35.148
don't look at her...

13:35.189 --> 13:36.483
This morning!

13:36.524 --> 13:39.736
And Dewey shoved a

13:36.524 --> 13:39.736
sandwich in the VCR!

13:39.778 --> 13:40.861
Malcolm, where is he?

13:40.903 --> 13:42.155
(quietly):

13:40.903 --> 13:42.155
Got to think.

13:42.196 --> 13:43.114
Diversion. Delancey.

13:43.156 --> 13:44.449
Delancey Park!

13:44.491 --> 13:45.784
He's meeting her

13:44.491 --> 13:45.784
at Delancey Park

13:45.824 --> 13:47.826
by the soccer field.

13:49.828 --> 13:51.748
Well...

13:51.790 --> 13:55.834
we'll just see what fate

13:51.790 --> 13:55.834
has in store for Francis.

14:06.179 --> 14:08.723
Francis, I have

14:06.179 --> 14:08.723
to tell you...

14:08.765 --> 14:10.891
Is Beebee coming?

14:08.765 --> 14:10.891
Yeah.

14:10.933 --> 14:13.186
But I have to tell you

14:10.933 --> 14:13.186
something first.

14:13.227 --> 14:15.896
I ratted you out to Mom.

14:13.227 --> 14:15.896
What?!

14:15.938 --> 14:17.148
I didn't mean to.

14:17.190 --> 14:18.899
Mom did... her eyes.

14:18.941 --> 14:20.109
And her voice, it was...

14:20.151 --> 14:21.611
I didn't mean to!

14:21.653 --> 14:24.071
Malcolm, how could you do that?

14:21.653 --> 14:24.071
I trusted you.

14:24.113 --> 14:25.699
I know.

14:25.740 --> 14:27.408
I'm sorry.

14:27.450 --> 14:29.160
Look, I sent her to the park.

14:29.202 --> 14:30.911
You've got an hour

14:29.202 --> 14:30.911
to get out of here

14:30.953 --> 14:31.954
and have a head start

14:30.953 --> 14:31.954
before she...

14:31.996 --> 14:33.914
Are you crazy?

14:31.996 --> 14:33.914
I can't go anywhere.

14:33.956 --> 14:35.958
Beebee's coming. Beebee.

14:36.000 --> 14:38.712
Francis, what's wrong with you?

14:38.753 --> 14:40.797
Why are you getting

14:38.753 --> 14:40.797
in so much trouble for her?

14:40.839 --> 14:41.756
You don't understand.

14:41.798 --> 14:43.924
Duh! No one understands.

14:43.966 --> 14:45.926
She's not nice,

14:43.966 --> 14:45.926
she's not smart,

14:45.968 --> 14:48.429
she's a thief, she's not even

14:45.968 --> 14:48.429
that good-looking.

14:48.471 --> 14:49.930
And, oh, guess what else.

14:49.972 --> 14:51.391
She treats you like crap!

14:51.432 --> 14:52.517
I know.

14:52.559 --> 14:54.310
You do?

14:54.352 --> 14:56.937
Of course I do.

14:56.979 --> 14:58.939
There's something

14:56.979 --> 14:58.939
you don't know about Beebee.

14:58.981 --> 15:00.900
What?

15:01.984 --> 15:04.779
That no one in her whole life

15:04.821 --> 15:07.114
has ever loved her

15:04.821 --> 15:07.114
the way that I do.

15:07.156 --> 15:09.784
All she has to do is see that

15:07.156 --> 15:09.784
and everything will change.

15:09.826 --> 15:13.329
I really thought he had

15:09.826 --> 15:13.329
something better.

15:13.371 --> 15:15.164
Look, Malcolm, you'll

15:13.371 --> 15:15.164
understand when you're older.

15:15.206 --> 15:17.417
Now, just go.

15:21.921 --> 15:22.963
What were you doing?

15:23.005 --> 15:24.965
Nothing.

15:23.005 --> 15:24.965
Mind your own business.

15:25.007 --> 15:27.968
Who were you talking to?

15:28.010 --> 15:30.680
I wasn't talking to anybody.

15:28.010 --> 15:30.680
You're imagining it.

15:30.722 --> 15:32.306
I heard you talking.

15:33.892 --> 15:36.394
Okay, I'll tell you.

15:36.436 --> 15:38.479
But you have to

15:36.436 --> 15:38.479
keep it a secret.

15:38.521 --> 15:40.440
You know the monster

15:38.521 --> 15:40.440
under your bed?

15:41.733 --> 15:42.983
It's called a Sasquatch.

15:43.025 --> 15:44.611
He hunts back there

15:43.025 --> 15:44.611
during the day.

15:44.652 --> 15:45.986
I was throwing him

15:44.652 --> 15:45.986
some raw meat

15:46.028 --> 15:47.697
so he wouldn't

15:46.028 --> 15:47.697
come get us tonight.

15:47.739 --> 15:50.283
I don't think

15:47.739 --> 15:50.283
I gave him enough.

15:50.324 --> 15:52.827
So, if I were you,

15:50.324 --> 15:52.827
I'd keep very quiet

15:52.869 --> 15:54.788
and stay the hell out of there.

15:54.829 --> 15:57.248
Get it?

16:10.678 --> 16:12.972
Move!

16:19.520 --> 16:21.731
BEEBEE:

16:19.520 --> 16:21.731
Francis?

16:25.944 --> 16:27.069
Beebee?

16:27.111 --> 16:28.321
Francis?

16:28.362 --> 16:29.322
Oh. Don't move.

16:29.363 --> 16:31.407
I want to remember this forever.

16:31.449 --> 16:32.700
Where are you?

16:32.742 --> 16:35.035
No! Don't look at me!

16:35.077 --> 16:37.037
I wanted so much

16:35.077 --> 16:37.037
to be perfect for you,

16:37.079 --> 16:39.415
but I couldn't find any soap.

16:39.457 --> 16:40.834
I'm hideous.

16:40.875 --> 16:42.627
Really?

16:40.875 --> 16:42.627
Yes.

16:42.669 --> 16:44.504
But it's okay.

16:44.545 --> 16:47.047
Everything is okay

16:44.545 --> 16:47.047
now that we're together.

16:47.089 --> 16:50.259
I can't tell you how beautiful

16:47.089 --> 16:50.259
you look at this moment.

16:50.301 --> 16:53.638
You look like an angel

16:50.301 --> 16:53.638
or a perfect dawn

16:53.680 --> 16:55.306
or a galaxy of stars.

16:55.348 --> 16:57.767
I don't think we should

16:55.348 --> 16:57.767
see each other anymore.

17:00.102 --> 17:03.105
And... my heart soars

17:00.102 --> 17:03.105
when I think of...

17:03.147 --> 17:04.565
Did you hear what I said?

17:05.358 --> 17:08.444
I... um...

17:08.486 --> 17:09.904
What?

17:09.946 --> 17:10.947
Look...

17:10.989 --> 17:12.699
you're a nice guy,

17:12.740 --> 17:15.493
and all those letters you sent--

17:12.740 --> 17:15.493
the stuff I understood, anyway--

17:15.535 --> 17:17.745
was sweet, but I don't know.

17:17.787 --> 17:20.080
Feels different now.

17:20.122 --> 17:22.000
It's hard to explain.

17:22.041 --> 17:24.377
Would you try?

17:24.418 --> 17:26.754
Well, maybe I just like

17:24.418 --> 17:26.754
the long-distance thing

17:26.796 --> 17:29.549
'cause, you know,

17:26.796 --> 17:29.549
you'd call and you'd talk

17:29.590 --> 17:31.926
and you'd make me feel

17:29.590 --> 17:31.926
so good about myself

17:31.968 --> 17:34.512
and I didn't have

17:31.968 --> 17:34.512
to do anything.

17:34.554 --> 17:36.096
Yeah, that's it.

17:36.138 --> 17:38.098
Beebee, please.

17:38.140 --> 17:39.976
I just think it's better

17:38.140 --> 17:39.976
we end it now

17:40.018 --> 17:41.310
before anybody gets hurt.

17:43.145 --> 17:46.524
I'm sorry, Francis.

17:50.653 --> 17:52.238
Ow.

17:53.656 --> 17:55.241
Ow!

17:56.158 --> 17:58.077
Ow!

17:59.161 --> 18:01.080
Ow!

18:02.081 --> 18:03.082
(yelling)

18:05.167 --> 18:07.086
(yelling continues)

18:08.379 --> 18:09.923
Get out of here!

18:09.964 --> 18:12.717
You stupid, dumb monster!

18:12.759 --> 18:14.385
(sobbing)

18:12.759 --> 18:14.385
This is my house!

18:14.427 --> 18:16.637
Ow.

18:14.427 --> 18:16.637
Go away!

18:16.679 --> 18:17.722
Ow!

18:17.764 --> 18:18.848
You leave me alone!

18:18.890 --> 18:20.558
Ow! Ow!

18:30.068 --> 18:32.152
You! You, there!

18:32.194 --> 18:33.320
What do you think

18:32.194 --> 18:33.320
you're doing?

18:33.362 --> 18:34.948
Excuse me?

18:34.989 --> 18:36.323
Do you know how dumb

18:34.989 --> 18:36.323
and careless you're being?

18:36.365 --> 18:38.158
Well, I brought...

18:38.200 --> 18:39.994
Oh, for God's sake,

18:38.200 --> 18:39.994
I'm not talking about that.

18:40.036 --> 18:41.370
But shame on you.

18:41.412 --> 18:43.205
Don't you know

18:41.412 --> 18:43.205
how this is all going to end?

18:43.247 --> 18:45.083
Do we know you?

18:45.124 --> 18:46.834
No, but I know you.

18:46.876 --> 18:48.168
You're young and pretty

18:48.210 --> 18:50.088
and you love to get

18:48.210 --> 18:50.088
16-year-old boys so twisted up

18:50.129 --> 18:51.881
they don't know

18:50.129 --> 18:51.881
what they're doing.

18:51.923 --> 18:53.340
And you think it's all in fun.

18:51.923 --> 18:53.340
You'll move on.

18:53.382 --> 18:54.842
You don't care

18:53.382 --> 18:54.842
how bad you hurt him.

18:54.884 --> 18:56.552
Let me tell you something,

18:54.884 --> 18:56.552
young lady.

18:56.594 --> 18:58.178
Hearts are precious things.

18:58.220 --> 19:00.264
You should be careful with them.

19:03.225 --> 19:04.644
You!

19:04.685 --> 19:05.979
You there!

19:06.020 --> 19:07.772
What do you think

19:06.020 --> 19:07.772
you're doing?!

19:07.814 --> 19:09.690
And then the monster

19:07.814 --> 19:09.690
started growling at me,

19:09.732 --> 19:11.275
so I threw rocks at him

19:09.732 --> 19:11.275
and I killed him.

19:11.317 --> 19:12.652
And then he started flying

19:11.317 --> 19:12.652
around on rocket boots,

19:12.693 --> 19:14.487
and I got to ride

19:12.693 --> 19:14.487
inside his head,

19:14.528 --> 19:16.572
and now the monster's my friend,

19:14.528 --> 19:16.572
and we went...

19:16.614 --> 19:18.198
and we went to get Slurpees.

19:18.240 --> 19:20.200
You did not!

19:18.240 --> 19:20.200
You're just lying!

19:20.242 --> 19:21.702
Reese, if that's what

19:20.242 --> 19:21.702
Dewey says happened,

19:21.744 --> 19:23.704
there's no reason

19:21.744 --> 19:23.704
to argue about it.

19:23.746 --> 19:26.206
No one believes I beat the

19:23.746 --> 19:26.206
last level of  Mortal Kombat.

19:26.248 --> 19:27.917
Because that's just ridiculous.

19:27.959 --> 19:29.418
No one beats Sub-Zero.

19:34.423 --> 19:36.300
Leave it off.

19:40.138 --> 19:42.222
So, Beebee broke up with me.

19:42.264 --> 19:44.224
Oh.

19:44.266 --> 19:45.518
You okay?

19:45.559 --> 19:47.478
I think I'm fine.

19:47.520 --> 19:50.397
There's a strange sense

19:47.520 --> 19:50.397
of peace that comes over you

19:50.439 --> 19:53.233
when you give up

19:50.439 --> 19:53.233
that last shred of dignity.

19:53.275 --> 19:55.235
It's nice.

19:55.277 --> 19:57.071
I'm really sorry.

19:57.113 --> 20:00.282
Well, if you're going

19:57.113 --> 20:00.282
to love women,

20:00.324 --> 20:02.869
you have to expect

20:00.324 --> 20:02.869
the occasional flaming wipeout.

20:02.910 --> 20:04.244
It's in the fine print,

20:04.286 --> 20:06.706
but you agree to it

20:04.286 --> 20:06.706
when you sign up.

20:06.747 --> 20:09.167
So what are you

20:06.747 --> 20:09.167
going to do?

20:09.208 --> 20:10.835
I'm going to go

20:09.208 --> 20:10.835
back to school.

20:10.877 --> 20:13.253
I only missed a day,

20:10.877 --> 20:13.253
so it shouldn't be too bad.

20:13.295 --> 20:14.714
There's a pack of farm girls

20:14.755 --> 20:17.133
that hang around

20:14.755 --> 20:17.133
outside the fence.

20:17.175 --> 20:19.552
Probably check that out.

20:19.593 --> 20:20.845
Later days.

20:20.887 --> 20:22.304
Wait.

20:22.346 --> 20:23.931
I'm sorry I ratted you out.

20:23.973 --> 20:25.058
I just got scared.

20:25.099 --> 20:26.059
Dude, it's ancient history.

20:26.100 --> 20:27.267
Don't worry about it.

20:27.309 --> 20:29.937
Well, can't you at least

20:27.309 --> 20:29.937
hit me or something,

20:29.979 --> 20:31.647
just so I feel like we're even?

20:31.689 --> 20:33.273
You want me to hit you?

20:33.315 --> 20:35.693
I don't know. Yeah.

20:35.735 --> 20:37.570
Okay.

20:40.364 --> 20:41.949
Thanks.

20:41.991 --> 20:42.992
Psych.

20:43.034 --> 20:44.077
Ow!

20:44.118 --> 20:45.828
Now we're even.

20:51.167 --> 20:52.585
Ow!

