Does it hurt?

21:35.377 --> 21:38.297
Oh, yeah.

21:39.548 --> 21:41.050
Well, son...

21:41.092 --> 21:44.053
you know, I wish I could

21:41.092 --> 21:44.053
say it gets easier,

21:44.095 --> 21:47.431
